title: 259: Conference Championship Preview
itunes:title: 259: Conference Championship Preview
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks preview the NFC (2:06) & (10:49) AFC title games by breaking down the key matchups and X-factors that could make a big difference on the field. The guys also reveal which declared underclassmen have them excited (20:45) and who they are watching this week at the East-West Shrine Game (25:55).
